Contact Us Today
Holiday Park is a wonderful place to live, work or play in Hallandale, Florida. It is the ideal Florida RV and manufactured home community with nearby attractions such as breathtaking beaches and Miami, Florida.
Whether it’s our convenient location or the array of amenities available, Holiday Park has what you’re looking for in an RV and manufactured home community.
We would like to hear from you and help you find the perfect home. Take the next important step and complete the contact form below. Don’t wait – contact us today!
3140 W Hallandale Beach Blvd.
Hallandale, FL 33009
(954) 981-4414
